{"tid":324413,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)2012 雷霆喪星 極樂帝國","createTime":"2017-07-16T12:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T18:31:09.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78d6179910165b06555a284dbdaea7221ea251c0","tid":324413,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=3i4YE5AD9HhR%2FjTKY5SYh54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7b72d1ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK或者加V台個網入白名單好似係<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=3i4YE5AD9HhR%2FjTKY5SYh54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ed4d9c34\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=3i4YE5AD9HhR%2FjTKY5SYh54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=807687a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/ac/2012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fac%2F2012.jpg&h=cef5deb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/70/Tropic_thunder_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F70%2FTropic_thunder_poster.jpg&h=f80736c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f9/Elysium_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff9%2FElysium_Poster.jpg&h=4bd378fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.2009年，太陽系九大行星經過幾千年的周期後排列成了一條直線，而太陽也進行了一場歷史上規模最大的太陽爆發。此時在地球，印度的梅加登銅礦場（世界最深的礦場），美國地理學家亞德里安&middot;哈姆斯里來到礦場接見了自己身爲天文地理學家的朋友薩特南，而薩特南卻爲亞德里安展示了一個驚人的事實：幾天前最大的太陽爆發導致中微子的數量到了無法測量的地步，而中微子甚至也開始對地球進行物理反應，開始加熱地球的核心，也會導致整個板塊全部崩潰！亞德里安一回華盛頓就去見了白宮參謀長卡爾&middot;安豪賽，卡爾在極爲震驚下而立刻將此事彙報給美國總統湯瑪斯&middot;威爾森。<br />\n<br />\n2.三位好萊塢巨星傻呼呼地去到東南亞荒蕪地帶拍戰爭片，可是，導演難以控制這班自我本位，喜歡擺架子的演員，於是絕情地將他們遺棄在一個聚集了毒品軍團的隱蔽森林，打算暗地拍攝一個戰爭片真人騷。三位巨星在森林中遇到真正的毒品軍團，以為自己正在演戲，為了爭奪奧斯卡最佳男主角獎，拚命與毒品軍團「對戰」，後來發覺事有蹺蹊，原來自己並非身處拍攝場地，而是真正的戰場！意外被迫面臨一場真正的戰爭，大家唯有假戲真做，硬個頭皮與敵軍對抗！<br />\n<br />\n3.2159年，世界分為兩種人，一種是富有的權貴，居住在可治癒任何疾病的人造宇宙都市極樂空間，[2]而其他人則居住在垃圾堆滿、惡臭難聞的地球，每一刻都面臨著死亡的危險。極樂空間國防部長羅茲為了保護該站居民的生活水平，奉行鐵血政策，嚴禁任何地球人來到人造太空站居住和移民，甚至不惜代價擊落所有企圖飛往極樂世界的飛船。馬克斯由於一次工廠工作的意外暴露在高量輻射中，只剩下五天的存活時間。為了治癒體內的高量輻射，他在朋友的幫助下，前往人造太空站，並阻止羅茲的鐵血政策..<br />\n<br />\n8 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK"},{"pid":"beded94fbb0906d9b6e0b94be4b9b4d524b65934","tid":324413,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea16922360bb5839f4e345168953b5b093b6ba96","tid":324413,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ef7424ad4cf264da9ff16b5af0f458b725faf4","tid":324413,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\